trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Transform" /> objects that can be individually accessed by index.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Media.Transform" /> que podem ser acessados individualmente por índice.

trans-unit.source: Except as noted, members of this class behave exactly as described by the <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection%601>, and <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> documentation.
trans-unit.target: Exceto conforme observado, os membros desta classe se comportam exatamente conforme descrito pelo <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IList%601>, <xref:System.Collections.Generic.ICollection%601>, e <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable%601> documentação.

trans-unit.source: **Freezable Features:** Because it inherits from the <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> class, the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TransformCollection> class provides several special features: <xref:System.Windows.Media.TransformCollection> objects can be declared as , shared among multiple objects, made read-only to improve performance, cloned, and made thread-safe.
trans-unit.target: **Recursos de Freezable:** porque ele herda do <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> classe, o <xref:System.Windows.Media.TransformCollection> classe fornece vários recursos especiais: <xref:System.Windows.Media.TransformCollection> objetos podem ser declarados como, compartilhados entre vários objetos, feitos somente leitura para melhorar desempenho, clonados e tornados thread-safe.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the different features provided by <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects, see the [Freezable Objects Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/freezable-objects-overview.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre os diferentes recursos fornecidos pelo <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objetos, consulte o [visão geral de objetos Freezable](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/freezable-objects-overview.md).
